data.description: Expansive 4-5 bedroom detached home nestled on a low traffic street in Mahanoy City. Features include hardwood floors, multiple fireplaces, security system, water treatment system, fenced in yard with pool & detached two-story carriage style garage. Welcoming you inside is a sun filled sitting room with a wall of windows. Large living room accompanied with a fireplace & French doors into the beautiful dining room. Designed with picture frame molding & beamed ceiling, it's the perfect space to host dinners. The kitchen offers ample cabinetry & gas cooking, followed by a fantastic heated enclosed porch for relaxing! Upstairs, there are 3 large bedrooms, office & full bath on the 2nd floor & 4th bedroom located in the walk up attic. Full basement provides ample storage & laundry. Fantastic outdoor space includes a bricked backyard perfect for entertaining. Detached garage used as rec room with a pool table included! Convenient location; minutes to schools, parks, shopping & more!
